| 9880      | 520   | No        |\\n| Pyerite   | 1235000   | 65000 | No        |\\n| Tritanium | 3458000   | 182000| No        |\\n| Zydrine   | 2470      | 130   | No        |\\n```\\nWe now have the extra `Waste` column.\\n\\nNow if we were to set _only_ `TE=20` then we would see that:\\n```\\n...\\nRun Time: 200\\n| Item      | Quantity  | Buildable |\\n|:---------:|:---------:|----------:|\\n| Isogen    | 26000     | No        |\\n| Megacyte  | 520       | No        |\\n| Mexallon  | 234000    | No        |\\n| Nocxium   | 10400     | No        |\\n| Pyerite   | 1300000   | No        |\\n| Tritanium | 3640000   | No        |\\n| Zydrine   | 2600      | No        |\\n```\\nWe can also use both with `ME=10` and `TE=20`:\\n```\\n...\\nRun Time: 200\\n| Item      | Quantity  | Buildable |\\n|:---------:|:---------:|----------:|\\n| Isogen    | 23400     | No        |\\n| Megacyte  | 468       | No        |\\n| Mexallon  | 210600    | No        |\\n| Nocxium   | 9360      | No        |\\n| Pyerite   | 1170000   | No        |\\n| Tritanium | 3276000   | No        |\\n| Zydrine   | 2340      | No        |\\n```'\"]", "timestamp": "2026-06-05 10:02:07", "level": "verbose", "process_id": 3366159, "thread_name": "MainThread"}
